{"tid":1507152,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"羅尚沛料恒指跌穿二萬五　勿博反彈！","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:01:00.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"be30008dd4d84c0adab252895acdb1dbc448fa8d","tid":1507152,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"恒指周一早間曾挫逾900點，技術上50天線短期很大機會跌穿250天線形成終極死亡交叉。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國銀河國際證券業務發展董事羅尚沛表示，港股技術走勢轉差，但更重要是基本因素轉壞，包括中美貿易關係惡化、聯儲局主席鮑威爾未有明確表示9月減息、人民幣匯率創新低、以及香港局勢不明朗等。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯一有機會正面一點的消息是，憧憬中國會否有刺激經濟措施出台，但暫時不似，故短期港股走勢仍差，恒指周一跌800點或差不多，但料短期未跌完，之後會穿一穿兩萬五關，投資者同時要留意離岸人民幣匯率會否失守7.2，繼而加劇股市跌勢。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他補充，恒指較後時間有機會進一步下試52周低位24,540點，現時除了短炒金礦股外不要手痕買貨，即使公用股也只是留意住先，不要胡亂博反彈。另外，當恒指處25,400點之上，進取投資者可考慮反手造淡。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"5962cdb83d07ce2d65eb0a306fb0c38cbf0a8ede","tid":1507152,"uid":47605,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjbVjJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjbVjJ3.jpg&h=4677b5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=da06a943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhSUAso.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhSUAso.jpg&h=aaca1d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=da06a943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"8c28bf2f16178f88a7f5692de545fe5dd51fcb59","tid":1507152,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:55:47.000